snippet.title: Early NekoNecro teaser (2019)
snippet.description:
Hand-drawn comic platformer starring Necro, the shapeshifting void we all know as a 'cat'.

50 levels, spanning five worlds, of pen and paper drawings that became pixels.

Music by Kevin MacLeod/Incompetech.
